<Layout title="Website Design & Management | Jake Fixes Tech — Littleton, NH"
description="Professional website design, hosting and management for small businesses. Packages starting at $750. Serving Littleton NH and the North Country.">

<!-- Header Banner -->
  <section style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;background-color:rgb(30,64,175);">
    <img src="/hero.jpg" alt="Professional tech workspace with dual monitors" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0;" />
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(30,64,175,0.88),rgba(37,99,235,0.88));z-index:1;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:56rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 1.5rem 4rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#93c5fd;">Web Services</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:white;margin-top:0.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Professional Website Design & Management</h1>
      <p style="color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto;">I build fast, modern, mobile-friendly websites for small businesses and organizations across the North Country. You own your site outright — no holding it hostage, no surprise fees.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Jake for Web Design -->
  <section style="background:#f8fafc;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#2563eb;">Why Jake Fixes Tech</p>
        <a href="/why-different" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;color:#2563eb;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;text-decoration:underline;">
  See why my sites beat old school web agencies →
</a>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:#111827;margin-top:0.5rem;">Websites Built for Real Businesses</h2>
        <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:0.75rem;max-width:36rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.75;">No bloated page builders, no monthly Squarespace fees. I build custom, lightning fast websites that you own outright — meaning the code, domain and content are yours forever.</p>
      </div>
      <div id="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Lightning Fast</h3>
          <p>Built with Astro and hosted on Cloudflare's global network. Your site loads instantly anywhere in the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">📱</div>
          <h3>Mobile First</h3>
          <p>Every site I build looks great on phones, tablets and desktops. Most of your visitors are on mobile.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">🔒</div>
          <h3>Secure & Reliable</h3>
          <p>Free SSL certificate, Cloudflare protection and 99.9% uptime. Your site is safe and always online.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">📍</div>
          <h3>Local & Personal</h3>
          <p>You're working directly with Jake — not an agency that hands you off to a junior developer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ADA + Scores Card -->
      <div class="ada-card">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          <div style="background:#16a34a;border-radius:50%;height:3rem;width:3rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
            <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">♿</span>
          </div>
